c: 4
v: 34
t: "Wor…ďe …ďen ko √Īii…ďu…ďe [e daŇčkiitagol] rew…ďe …ďen, sabu ko Alla ∆Āurniri kon yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore yoga, e sabu kon ko wintii e jawle ma…ď…ďe. [rew…ďe] mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen, ko yaŇčkinii…ďe reenotoo…ďe ka wirnii, sabu kon ko Alla Reenini …ďe.∆Āen [rew…ďe] …ďe huloton dartagol(cuwtagol) mun : waajee…ďe, feron…ďe ka nda…ó…óudiiji, piyon…ďe. Si …ďe …óoftike on, wata on a…ď…ďir e dow ma…ď…ďe laawol ! Pellet, Alla Laatike Toowu…óo, Maw…óo"